"{\"uid\": \"asiaone.com-singapore-i-am-completely-overwhelmed-olympic-medallist-max-maeder-receives-rousing-welcome-upon\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"SINGAPORE - The arrival hall at Changi Airport Terminal 3 was busier than usual and crackled with anticipation before dawn on Aug 13 as Singapore welcomed its youngest Olympic medallist, kitefoiler Maximilian Maeder, back home.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999995698559375, \"rank\": 4.1990988182284126e-07, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the close to 60 people that received 17-year-old Maximilian and fellow sailor Ryan Lo, 27, who competed in the men's dinghy event, were a handful of supporters, Minister for Culture, Community and Youth Edwin Tong, officials from Singapore Sailing Federation and Sport Singapore and about 20 members of the media.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lo\", \"score\": 0.9999774267436199, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Lo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lo\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edwin_Tong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Edwin Tong\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edwin_Tong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edwin_Tong\"}, {\"begin\": 465, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Sailing_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Singapore Sailing Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Sailing_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Sailing_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maximilian is Singapore's youngest Olympic medallist after he finished third in the men's kite event on Aug 9.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999995698559375, \"rank\": 4.1990988182284126e-07, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His bronze medal came on the same day that Singapore celebrated its 59th year of independence and also ended an eight-year wait to see a Singaporean on an Olympic podium since swimmer Joseph Schooling won gold in 2016.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999995698559375, \"rank\": 4.1990988182284126e-07, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"score\": 0.5643644067870435, \"rank\": 0.7719040947684463, \"text\": \"Singaporean\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\"}, {\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joseph Schooling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most had arrived as early as 5.30am, before Maximilian walked into the arrival hall after his near 13-hour flight from Paris on Singapore Airlines flight SQ335.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998400785571, \"rank\": 1.5992154006836484e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Airlines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Singapore Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Airlines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the crowd shouted, \\\"Welcome home, Max\\\", Mr Tong placed a garland around his neck.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"score\": 0.999893811563176, \"rank\": 0.000104267967385963, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tong_Jian\", \"score\": 0.9996331542105922, \"rank\": 0.00036698041483930764, \"text\": \"Tong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tong_Jian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tong_Jian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am completely overwhelmed,\\\" said Maximilian as he puffed his cheeks.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As he obliged to every autograph or wefie request, he remarked: \\\"This is so sweet.\\\"\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans here had been eager to express their gratitude for the timely birthday gift he had given the nation just days before.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maximilian had made history on Aug 9 by securing a bronze medal at the Paris Olympics, putting Singapore firmly on the sporting map.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999995698559375, \"rank\": 4.1990988182284126e-07, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Caleb Tan, 6, was one of the young supporters who turned up to receive Maximilian.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\", \"score\": 0.9998053687715363, \"rank\": 0.0001943748951112223, \"text\": \"Caleb\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\"}, {\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He carried a self-made poster that read, \\\"I skipped school to see Max Maeder\\\".\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"score\": 0.999893811563176, \"rank\": 0.000104267967385963, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Caleb said he worked on it with his mum.\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He got more than what he wished for - Maximilian's autograph on the poster - as he was also hoisted onto the Olympic medallist's shoulders for photos.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"I was so happy when he won a bronze medal because he tried his best.\\\"\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Caleb's mother Wendy Tan, a 35-year-old financial consultant, said: \\\"Max is an inspiration.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2050, \"end\": 2053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"score\": 0.999893811563176, \"rank\": 0.000104267967385963, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He speaks so well on TV and I really liked how he thanks his parents.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The respect he has for people is great too and that is important to teach the young kids.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want Caleb to understand that so I took him here to see the man himself.\\\"\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A 39-year-old researcher who wanted to be known only as Jean, took her three young kids Serena, 10, Ashton, 7 and Elijah, 5, to welcome Maximilian.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 0.9999732151690448, \"rank\": 2.437771739999849e-05, \"text\": \"Serena\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 2412, \"end\": 2418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Ashton\", \"score\": 0.8959687294879706, \"rank\": 0.1161103809631019, \"text\": \"Ashton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Ashton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Ashton\"}, {\"begin\": 2426, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.666226754647344e-16, \"text\": \"Elijah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\"}, {\"begin\": 2448, \"end\": 2458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jean said: \\\"We watched most of Team Singapore in action as a family, sometimes from highlights if the events start late.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2497, \"end\": 2506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999995698559375, \"rank\": 4.1990988182284126e-07, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are very excited to be here and it was actually the kids who saw Instagram and told me Max is arriving at this hour today.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2650, \"end\": 2659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7350536060280287e-21, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"score\": 0.999893811563176, \"rank\": 0.000104267967385963, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of the reasons I agreed is because it is such a historic moment to be here and to thank him in person.\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has helped young kids realise that as a Singaporean, they can make it to the world stage and that we may be from a little red dot, but we can make a big impact too.\\\"\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2860, \"end\": 2871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"score\": 0.5643644067870435, \"rank\": 0.7719040947684463, \"text\": \"Singaporean\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ashton had brought along a piece of paper in hopes of snagging an autograph from Maximilian while Serena was looking to have a photo with the Olympic hero.\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2987, \"end\": 2993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Ashton\", \"score\": 0.8959687294879706, \"rank\": 0.1161103809631019, \"text\": \"Ashton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Ashton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Ashton\"}, {\"begin\": 3068, \"end\": 3078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 3085, \"end\": 3091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 0.9999732151690448, \"rank\": 2.437771739999849e-05, \"text\": \"Serena\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also present was\\u00a0Afiq Azman.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old said he started watching Maximilian only in the final and was here to \\\"soak in the atmosphere\\\".\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3214, \"end\": 3224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9822045280797692, \"rank\": 0.017751175938634917, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Afiq said: \\\"I knew when it was gearing towards the final that there might be a chance we could get a medal.\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no better storybook ending than Singapore winning a medal on National Day.\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3436, \"end\": 3445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999995698559375, \"rank\": 4.1990988182284126e-07, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today is my day off and it is a rare occasion to experience this in Singapore.\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3549, \"end\": 3558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999995698559375, \"rank\": 4.1990988182284126e-07, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just here to soak in the atmosphere and thank him personally.\\\"\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ:A love for winning and curry puffs: Things to know about Singapore's youngest Olympic medalist Max Maeder  Thisarticlewas first published inThe Straits Times.\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3698, \"end\": 3707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9999995698559375, \"rank\": 4.1990988182284126e-07, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 3736, \"end\": 3739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"score\": 0.999893811563176, \"rank\": 0.000104267967385963, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Branning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Permission required for reproduction.\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3837, \"entities\": []}]}"